{"tid":2488233,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警員張展宏出庭指證青年藏卡片摺刀 作供稱：唔記得、答唔到你、唔知去咗邊 主控不禁怨言：你而家作緊供，大佬！","createTime":"2021-04-14T05:52:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T06:51:34.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"6b2057733190f087c593f92a7afe7666dca8ca36","tid":2488233,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T05:52:00.000Z","msg":"職訓局青年書院女生陳彥霖離世8個月當天，警方在青年書院附近商場截查19歲青年，在他的銀包內搜出一把黑色卡片摺刀。青年被控在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器，案件今於觀塘裁判法院開審，惟出庭作供的警員對控方提問一時支吾以對，一時低頭沉思，更謂「太耐，好難答到你」，檢控官不禁加重語氣喝斥指「警員，你依家作緊供嘅，大佬！」<br />\n<br />\n將軍澳刑事調查隊警員1355張展宏應傳召出庭作供，辯方首先問他的書面供詞是否有需要作出修改，張稱只需修改某處的時間；辯方再問是否還有其他地方需要修改，張答「暫時睇唔到」。辯方指出，張在口供中聲稱拍攝了6張相片，但控方只提供了5張，張稱已記不起。<br />\n<br />\n其後被告透過手機向李展示參加童軍時的照片，並解釋摺刀的用途，但李並沒有聽取解釋，只說「都唔似你嘅」；李庭上否認，並謂「我唔會咁樣同佢講」。<br />\n<br />\n辯方續指，張當日曾參與搜屋，惟呈堂文件卻不見有被告簽署的書面同意書，張稱可能記載於警員記事冊內，然後應辯方要求即時翻閱，惟不得要領。張其後解釋「唔記得、答唔到你、唔知去咗邊。」<br />\n<br />\n控方其後要求張澄清辯方所指的消失相片，問究竟是6張還是5張，張支吾以對，又低頭沉思，然後一邊翻閱相冊一邊說：「相片簿唔係我整，太耐，好難答到你」，檢控官按捺不住，加重語氣喝斥「警員，你而家作緊供嘅，大佬！」<br />\n<br />\n控方另追問搜屋同意書，張回應：「因為太耐，可能其他同事記事冊有寫，點解冇提堂，答唔到」；檢控官再問他可曾有處理，張稱：「太耐，冇乜印象，可能唔係我處理。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210414/QS65QATXSNCLHFYOZRRTD2QL24/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210414%2FQS65QATXSNCLHFYOZRRTD2QL24%2F&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1TvbkzvtmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=0f97b9a3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210414%2FQS65QATXSNCLHFYOZRRTD2QL24%2F&h=5e6b1c10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210414/QS65QATXSNCLHFYOZRRTD2QL24/</a>"},{"pid":"e3080f698fc04e44886a62651fb17f415325032f","tid":2488233,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T05:54:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74b2e8d4402d9df2f816c611a7bc0f95b3511e5e","tid":2488233,"uid":65888,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T05:54:49.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1646f08ea254a23193a3e9661d70bd1b9f0b1b6b","tid":2488233,"uid":230530,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T05:55:16.000Z","msg":"邊個官？想調去守水塘？"},{"pid":"06aa6da644a5bc9246c9e311f23d894e1534b9d2","tid":2488233,"uid":39838,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T05:59:08.000Z","msg":"hea 到咁想幫佢講「電光火石間口供同現實有出入好正常」都幫唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"545d02b30381e82e5efaec9ed63de7a709231380","tid":2488233,"uid":10322,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T06:02:05.000Z","msg":"控方問既都答成咁??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20b60c80e31dccd35c2d27769c75f441dbe249b5","tid":2488233,"uid":66324,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"545d02b30381e82e5efaec9ed63de7a709231380","tid":2488233,"uid":10322,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T06:02:05.000Z","msg":"控方問既都答成咁??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T06:03:35.000Z","msg":"有乜所謂, 反正入硬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/vampire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aae7348237a19bf089d0b11ce2e0258ebf5be566","tid":2488233,"uid":364068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"202